data.description: This charming ranch-style home is squeaky clean and ready for you to see. Walk into the inviting entryway and you'll be greeted by the living room with plush carpeting and large windows letting in natural light. The open kitchen features newer appliances and a view of the partially fenced-in backyard. Each of the three bedrooms in this home feature cozy carpeting and plenty of closet space. The primary en suite showcases new flooring and a generous vanity. The bonus family room of this home includes a fireplace and access to the four-seasons room. Bonus amenities of this home include a spacious back patio that's perfect for entertaining, main floor laundry, and an attached two-car garage.
